videos.headline: Greene finds open green for the end zone
videos.description: Bowling Green's Travis Greene finds an open hole and then jukes out a defender with a sweet jab-step to reach the end zone and put the Falcons up 21-0.

videos.headline: Bowling Green keeps rolling with 45-yard TD
videos.description: Facing a third-and-three, Bowling Green runs a play-action to perfection, hitting Roger Lewis for a 45-yard touchdown strike increasing the Falcons' lead to 28-0.
